{
  "page": "Lord Renly's Ride",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Serena_Malyon_Lord_Renly%27s_Ride.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/29/Serena_Malyon_Lord_Renly%27s_Ride.jpg/350px-Serena_Malyon_Lord_Renly%27s_Ride.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"366\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/29/Serena_Malyon_Lord_Renly%27s_Ride.jpg/525px-Serena_Malyon_Lord_Renly%27s_Ride.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/29/Serena_Malyon_Lord_Renly%27s_Ride.jpg/700px-Serena_Malyon_Lord_Renly%27s_Ride.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Serena_Malyon_Lord_Renly%27s_Ride.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>\"Lord Renly's Ride\", by Serena Malyon © FFG</div></div></div>\n<p>\"<b>Lord Renly's Ride</b>\" is a song written by <a href=\"/index.php/Hamish_the_Harper\" title=\"Hamish the Harper\">Hamish the Harper</a>, for <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_Wedding\" title=\"Purple Wedding\">the wedding</a> of King <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey I</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Margaery_Tyrell\" title=\"Margaery Tyrell\">Margaery Tyrell</a>.\n</p><p>The lyrics narrate how <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">Renly Baratheon</a>'s ghost repents from his attempt to usurp <a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">his nephew</a>. He defies the  <a href=\"/index.php/Stranger_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Stranger (the Seven)\">Lord of Death</a>, returns to the land of the living to defend the realm from <a href=\"/index.php/Stannis_Baratheon\" title=\"Stannis Baratheon\">Stannis Baratheon</a>, and then flies to <a href=\"/index.php/Highgarden\" title=\"Highgarden\">Highgarden</a> to see his true love's face one last time.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>In reality, \"Renly's ghost\" was Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Garlan_Tyrell\" title=\"Garlan Tyrell\">Garlan Tyrell</a>, who wore Renly's armor during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Blackwater\" title=\"Battle of the Blackwater\">Battle of the Blackwater</a>, on the suggestion of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Petyr_Baelish\" title=\"Petyr Baelish\">Petyr Baelish</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Lyrics\">Lyrics</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Renly%27s_Ride&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Lyrics\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"font-style:italic;padding-left:1em;display:flow-root;\" class=\"poem\">\n<p>From his throne of bones the <a href=\"/index.php/Stranger_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Stranger (the Seven)\">Lord of Death</a> looked down on the <a href=\"/index.php/Renly_Baratheon\" title=\"Renly Baratheon\">murdered lord</a>...<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Renly%27s_Ride&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos60.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_60\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 60\">Chapter 60</a>, Tyrion VIII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_67\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 67\">Chapter 67</a>, Jaime VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403195702\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.025 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.027 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 254/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8666/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1111/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 220/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 10/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 1/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1472/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   14.824      1 -total\n 68.43%   10.144      3 Template:Ref\n 45.54%    6.751      3 Template:Ref/core\n 23.84%    3.534      1 Template:Lyrics\n 18.69%    2.770      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:4866-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403195702 and revision id 276521\n --